Subject: Sculpt Object converter
Date:    Thursday, 01 December 1994 20:12:32 
From:    Patrick Sauvageau <sauvp@citi.doc.ca>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  


For those who want to convert Sculpt object to imagine, i have a good
utility to do that. It is called Xobject. It can read Sculpt and Videoscape
and convert it to Imagine format. (Turbo-silver in fact). 

Since i lost the original archive, the archive i have is not in the
original form the author wanted it to be. However, the shareware
information and the full documentation is included. Because of that, this
archive cannot be put on aminet or on any public distribution systems

Anybody interested in this utility, send me a mail. 
The archive is just 15k and it need arp.library.




