  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  



> Well, I've just figured out the new smart bones. It works great, but
> with one amazing twist: the Make Big Bones and Make Small Bones are
> backwards, at least in the Amiga version. Hard to believe such an error
> but after spending 2 hours trying to make a bending finger I looked
> carefully at the subgroups and realized that whenever I chose Make SM
> Bones it marked it just the other way around, with the result that the
> bending looked extremely angular. I would really like someone else to
