When you get as big as Intel you no longer need to
care about your customers who are already enslaved
by the Intel/MicroSloth architecture.

>my Pentium approximately 3 months ago, and it has the bug.  That is pretty rece
nt.

It takes a while for the distribution channels to
run their course.  We just got a couple of new ALR
servers that exhibit the bug, too.
 
