In issue 43 of Amiga shopper they do a comparison (roughly) between a
standard A4000 and a Raptor. They used lightwave, not imagine, but the
following should still hold true.
The simple object scenes rendered with little speed increase. However When
they started (bench mark 4) raytracing complex scenes, thats when the
differences were logrthmic.
Therefore I think we need a complex scene to show the real speed
differences.
