The DXF import/export on Imagine prior to 3.1 is not very robust. IM31 fixed
all that - it is one of the most solid DXF file converters I've encountered.
Other than that, your only option is Interchange or Pixel 3D - if you're dos
bound, you will have to wait for Interchange (windoz), coming your way soon.



